JIRA Version = Atlassian JIRA (v4.4-m6#642-r152482)

I am getting "Response is not well-formed XML." error when I try to post comment using SOAP API using an ASP.NET 2.0 web application. The sample code is pasted below the error line is "myCompanyJiraService.addComment(myToken, "WEB-576", myComment);". Can you please help me ASAP, we need to launch JIRA which is integrated with our other apps. The same code works fine with Atlassian JIRA (v4.3.3#617-r149616).

{code}
    string commentBody = "hello";
    MyCompanyJIRA.JiraSoapServiceService myCompanyJiraService = new MyCompanyJIRA.JiraSoapServiceService();
    String myToken = myCompanyJiraService.login("user_name", "password");
    MyCompanyJIRA.RemoteComment myComment = new MyCompanyJIRA.RemoteComment();
    myComment.body = commentBody;

    MyCompanyJIRA.RemoteComment[] comments = myCompanyJiraService.getComments(myToken, "WEB-576");
    bool commentDuplicate = false;
    foreach (MyCompanyJIRA.RemoteComment comment in comments)
    {
        if (comment.author.Equals("user_name") && comment.body.Equals(commentBody))
        {
            commentDuplicate = true;
            break;
        }
    }
    if (!commentDuplicate)
        myCompanyJiraService.addComment(myToken, "WEB-576", myComment);
{code}

